AWS Budget

The first thing you want to do with any AWS account especially a new one is to set a budget.

Steps:
1) Open your AWS Console
2) Go to AWS cost explorer.
3) Go to create budget
4) Select Cost budget
5) Click on set budget
6) Fill in the fields: name, start date, recurring, fixed amount, every service
7) Click on configure threshold
8) Set threshold based on actual cost and input alert threshold(a very low amount is advised)
9) Add an email to receive the alerts
10)Review and Click on create 
